                            <comment id="16073551" author="davsclaus" created="Tue, 4 Jul 2017 12:11:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Try with newer version of Camel as 2.16.x is EOL&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16073558" author="chirag0103" created="Tue, 4 Jul 2017 12:15:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I did try with 2.18.1 too. It doesn&apos;t work either.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16073599" author="chirag0103" created="Tue, 4 Jul 2017 12:39:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also tried using the version 2.19.0, didn&apos;t work. Can you help me out here?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16074475" author="davsclaus" created="Wed, 5 Jul 2017 09:21:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There was an issue in the paging now using the count and page options&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But when its fixed you can then retrieve more data, such as 50 etc.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;from(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;twitter-timeline:user?type=polling&amp;amp;user=cameltweet&amp;amp;sinceId=1&amp;amp;count=50&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
